sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User
    participant UI as Streamlit UI
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant State as Workflow State
    participant R as Research Agent
    participant O as Outreach Agent
    participant M as Monitoring Module
    participant D as Risk Detection Agent
    participant RC as Recovery Agent

    User->>UI: Run workflow with company name
    UI->>Orch: run_sales_workflow(initial_state)

    Orch->>R: run(state)
    R-->>Orch: Enriched company context
    Orch->>State: Update with research outputs

    Orch->>O: run(state)
    O-->>Orch: Initial outreach email
    Orch->>State: Update email fields

    Orch->>M: run(state)
    M-->>Orch: Engagement status + inactivity days
    Orch->>State: Update monitoring fields

    Orch->>D: run(state)
    D-->>Orch: Risk level + reason
    Orch->>State: Update risk fields

    Orch->>RC: run(state)
    RC-->>Orch: Recovery strategy + follow-up email
    Orch->>State: Update recovery outputs

    Orch-->>UI: final_state + logs
    UI-->>User: Dashboard sections + decision trace
